messages.text: I keep getting these strange hangup calls.
Like, how many times has it happened?
At first every so often. Now like one or two times a day!
The first few times I thought it might be a mistake.
And you have no idea who it is?
You know there’s websites where you can trace phone #s.
The ID always shows up as unknown
Maybe it’s someone playing a prank on you.
This is the lamest prank ever.
Ok, this is starting to sound weird.
This is like those crime shows
Where girls are harassed by stalkers
I saw one where this girl befriended this killer online
I’m just saying, it’s so sketchy
I don’t know what else to do.
Did you tell anybody else about it?
I’m too embarrassed to tell anyone else
Don’t worry ok. I’ll stay on the phone with you.
I was going to hang out with Devon tonight but this is important.
Jen I’M SO SCARED. ARE YOU THERE?
I’m so scared. The # called again. This creepy voice said they’re going to KILL ME.
We don’t need to do that
The police don’t need to be involved.
But they said they’re going to KILL you!
it could be a prank. Like you said.
Mia i don’t get it. this is scary
you don’t want to do anything about it?
This scary stuff is going on!
You said this has been going on for two weeks?
Before or after we all went to the beach?
It’s got to be one or the other.
You started acting really weird before we left.
Are you sure it wasn’t before?
What is really going on Mia
What do you mean they’re not real?
Ever since you and Devon got together that day at the beach we haven’t been hanging out.
I feel like I’m losing my best friend.
I thought if I made this up then you’d have to be there for me again.
This is so messed up Mia.
Why not just talk to me
Instead of making up this crazy story?
I’m sorry if you felt like I deserted you
I shouldn’t be so jealous of your relationship.
Theres nothing that will make me stop being friends with you k?
ill try spending more time with you for sure.
I’ll talk to you later k?
I just got a hang-up call from an unknown #.
